data.description: Look no further.  This lovingly maintained end unit townhome features 2 bedrooms and a loft. 2.1 bath and a 2 car garage.  It has an open floor plan that combines the living and dining room.  Cozy up in the living room with a gas fireplace perfect for cold nights.  The lower level can be used as an office or playroom.  There is a private balcony that has a partial view of the lake.  HVAC and siding has been replaced.  All appliances stay.
